{{LGBT rights}}
'''LGBT權益反对派'''是反對[[女同性戀|女同性戀]]，[[男同性戀者|男同性戀者]]，[[双性恋|双性恋]]和[[跨性別|跨性別]]能獲得法律平等保障和對待的[[自然權利|權利]]。

反對的原因各不相同，有的是基於[[歧視|歧視]]或者认为给予性少数者平等权利会形成[[逆向歧视|逆向歧视]]。有的担心对[[家庭|家庭]]价值、[[性别分工|性别分工]]和社会文化的冲击。

还有立足于[[宗教|宗教]]、[[道德|道德]]等观点，或者因为自身[[同性恋恐惧症|恐同]]、[[跨性別恐懼症|恐跨]]、[[偏执|偏执]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vexen.co.uk/religion/homosexuality.html#Islam|title=Homosexuality and Religion|quote=Lillian Ladele contined {{sic}} to fight, and the case eventually went to the European Court of Human Rights, where, on the 15th of Jan 2013, they also found that anti-gay bigotry was not excused in the public sector, not even by domineering Christians.|accessdate=2017-01-19|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304023246/http://www.vexen.co.uk/religion/homosexuality.html#Islam|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[仇恨|仇恨]]<ref name=opinion>{{cite court |litigants= Romer v. Evans |vol=517 |reporter=U.S.  |opinion=620  |pinpoint= |court= |date= 1996 |url= http://caselaw.lp.findlaw.com/scripts/getcase.pl?court=US&vol=000&invol=U10179 |accessdate= |quote=}}</ref>、对[[意識形態|意識形態]]的警惕、或其他因素而反对。

反对团体完全反對或部分反对的LGBT權益的一般包括[[同性婚姻|同性婚姻]]、[[民事結合|民事結合]]、[[LGBT撫養|LGBT撫養]]和[[LGBT收養|收養]]、[[性傾向和兵役|兵役]]、[[性別重置手術|性別重置手術]]等多个议题。

== 公眾意見 ==
在所有的社會中，都有各自對於適當和不適當的[[性規範|性規範]]，有些文化認可同性愛情和性慾，有些文化則採取壓抑的姿態。<ref>Murray, Stephen O., ''Homosexualities'', University of Chicago 2000</ref>

== 宗教因素 ==
{{Main|宗教與同性戀}}
許多形式的宗教，鼓動其信徒反對LGBT權益，像是[[福音主義|福音主義]]<ref>Strauss, Lehman, Litt.D., F.R.G.S. [http://www.bible.org/page.asp?page_id=1302 "Homosexuality: The Christian Perspective"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bible.org/page.asp?page_id=1302 |date=20070415203635 }}.</ref>、 [[天主教|天主教]]<ref>[http://www.religioustolerance.org/hom_rom.htm "Roman Catholics and Homosexuality"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.religioustolerance.org/hom_rom.htm |date=20170317054718 }}, Ontario Consultants on Religious Tolerance (2006)</ref>、[[摩爾門教|摩爾門教]]<ref>[http://www.lds.org/hf/library/0,16866,4266-1,00.html?LibraryURL=/lds/hf/display "Teaching about Procreation and Chastity: Homosexuality"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lds.org/hf/library/0,16866,4266-1,00.html?LibraryURL=%2Flds%2Fhf%2Fdisplay |date=20130501122253 }}, The Church of Jesus-Christ of Latter-day Saints. Home & Family.</ref>、[[猶太教正統派|猶太教正統派]]<ref>Shafran, Rabbi Avi. [http://www.jlaw.com/Commentary/maritalprob.html "Jewish Law: Marital Problems"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.jlaw.com/Commentary/maritalprob.html |date=20161006153527 }}. Jewish Law Commentary: Examining Halacha, Jewish Issues, and Secular Law.</ref>、[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]<ref>[http://www.religioustolerance.org/hom_isla1.htm "Islam and Homosexuality"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.religioustolerance.org/hom_isla1.htm |date=20170317055607 }}, Ontario Consultants on Religious Tolerance (2005).</ref>等。{{citation needed|這些宗教團體認為同性之間的性行為，視為宗教上的一種[[罪_(宗教)|罪]]，並聲稱支持LGBT權益會削弱社會的道德標準。}}

